type. Set to 0x00000003 for the MONTHLYDATE trigger type.</p><p><b>Days (4 bytes): </b>Bit flags that specify on
which days of the month the trigger fires, which are interpreted as specified
in section <a href="593fa1fc-92ed-4d80-9992-d166299482dd" data-linktype="relative-path">2.4.2.11.2</a>. </p><p><b>Months (2 bytes): </b>Bit flags that specify on
